they experienced while fighting.

25:51.147 --> 25:53.382
(GENTLE MUSIC)

25:53.384 --> 25:55.183
Talking about it helps.

25:55.185 --> 25:57.251
(GENTLE MUSIC)

25:57.253 --> 26:00.756
