26:43.099 --> 26:44.234
I wanna die.

26:45.970 --> 26:46.834
What?

26:46.836 --> 26:48.105
I want to die.

26:50.708 --> 26:52.708
I don't believe you.

26:52.710 --> 26:54.308
I don't give a shit if you do.

26:54.310 --> 26:56.978
