26:59.450 --> 27:00.317
Get out.

27:01.251 --> 27:02.116
We're done here.

27:02.118 --> 27:02.985
Ronnie I...

27:02.987 --> 27:04.186
Get out!

27:04.188 --> 27:06.858
(GENTLE MUSIC)

